<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rental Agreement</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .clause {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .signature-section {
            margin-top: 50px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .signature-box {
            text-align: center;
            width: 45%;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
            width: 200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .parties-section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .witness-section {
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="title">RENTAL AGREEMENT</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        This Rental Agreement is made on {{ current_date }} between:
    </div>

    <div class="parties-section">
        <strong>LANDLORD/LESSOR:</strong><br>
        Name: {{ landlord_name or "[Landlord's Full Name]" }}<br>
        Father's/Husband's Name: {{ landlord_father_name or "[Father's/Husband's Name]" }}<br>
        Address: {{ landlord_address or "[Landlord's Complete Address]" }}<br>
        Phone: {{ landlord_phone or "[Landlord's Phone Number]" }}<br>
        Email: {{ landlord_email or "[Landlord's Email]" }}<br>
        (Hereinafter referred to as "LANDLORD")
    </div>

    <div class="parties-section">
        <strong>TENANT/LESSEE:</strong><br>
        Name: {{ tenant_name or "[Tenant's Full Name]" }}<br>
        Father's/Husband's Name: {{ tenant_father_name or "[Father's/Husband's Name]" }}<br>
        Address: {{ tenant_address or "[Tenant's Complete Address]" }}<br>
        Phone: {{ tenant_phone or "[Tenant's Phone Number]" }}<br>
        Email: {{ tenant_email or "[Tenant's Email]" }}<br>
        (Hereinafter referred to as "TENANT")
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <strong>PROPERTY DETAILS:</strong><br>
        The property located at: {{ property_address or "[Complete Property Address]" }}<br>
        Type: {{ property_type or "[Apartment/House/Commercial Space]" }}<br>
        Area: {{ property_area or "[Area in sq ft]" }}<br>
        Furnishing: {{ furnishing_status or "[Furnished/Semi-Furnished/Unfurnished]" }}
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <strong>TERMS AND CONDITIONS:</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>1. RENT:</strong> The monthly rent for the said property is Rs. {{ monthly_rent or "[Monthly Rent Amount]" }}/- (Rupees {{ rent_in_words or "[Rent in Words]" }} only) payable on or before {{ rent_due_date or "5th" }} of each month.
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>2. SECURITY DEPOSIT:</strong> The tenant has paid a security deposit of Rs. {{ security_deposit or "[Security Deposit Amount]" }}/- (Rupees {{ deposit_in_words or "[Deposit in Words]" }} only) which shall be refunded at the time of vacating the premises after deducting any dues.
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>3. LEASE PERIOD:</strong> This agreement is for a period of {{ lease_period or "[Lease Duration]" }} commencing from {{ start_date or "[Start Date]" }} and ending on {{ end_date or "[End Date]" }}.
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>4. MAINTENANCE:</strong> {{ maintenance_clause or "The tenant shall maintain the property in good condition and shall be responsible for minor repairs. Major structural repairs shall be borne by the landlord." }}
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>5. UTILITIES:</strong> {{ utilities_clause or "Electricity, water, gas, and other utility charges shall be borne by the tenant." }}
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>6. SUBLETTING:</strong> The tenant shall not sublet or transfer the tenancy rights to any third party without written consent of the landlord.
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>7. TERMINATION:</strong> Either party may terminate this agreement by giving {{ notice_period or "30" }} days written notice to the other party.
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>8. RENEWAL:</strong> This agreement may be renewed by mutual consent of both parties with revised terms if any.
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>9. LEGAL JURISDICTION:</strong> Any disputes arising out of this agreement shall be subject to the jurisdiction of courts at {{ jurisdiction or "[City Name]" }}.
    </div>

    <div class="clause">
        <strong>10. ADDITIONAL TERMS:</strong><br>
        {{ additional_terms or "[Any additional terms and conditions agreed upon by both parties]" }}
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        Both parties have read and understood all the terms and conditions mentioned above and agree to abide by them.
    </div>

    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div><strong>LANDLORD</strong></div>
            <div>{{ landlord_name or "[Landlord's Name]" }}</div>
            <div>Date: {{ current_date }}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-box">
            <div class="signature-line"></div>
            <div><strong>TENANT</strong></div>
            <div>{{ tenant_name or "[Tenant's Name]" }}</div>
            <div>Date: {{ current_date }}</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="witness-section">
        <strong>WITNESSES:</strong><br><br>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
            <div>
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <div><strong>Witness 1</strong></div>
                <div>Name: {{ witness_1_name or "[Witness 1 Name]" }}</div>
                <div>Address: {{ witness_1_address or "[Witness 1 Address]" }}</div>
                <div>Phone: {{ witness_1_phone or "[Witness 1 Phone]" }}</div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="signature-line"></div>
                <div><strong>Witness 2</strong></div>
                <div>Name: {{ witness_2_name or "[Witness 2 Name]" }}</div>
                <div>Address: {{ witness_2_address or "[Witness 2 Address]" }}</div>
                <div>Phone: {{ witness_2_phone or "[Witness 2 Phone]" }}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
